# --- Browser automation guard (no Playwright/Cypress/etc. in this repo) ---
# Screenshot capture is external — these patterns prevent accidental local
# artifacts from being committed if an external tool is run from inside the
# repo. The rule itself is documented in docs/screenshots/README.md.
playwright.config.*
playwright-report/
test-results/
/e2e/
**/*.spec.ts-snapshots/
**/*.test.ts-snapshots/

# --- Screenshot capture baseline (external tool writes here) ---
# Full-capture PNGs + report are produced by drmirror-screenshooter and
# not tracked in this repo. Per-phase PNGs under phase-A/, phase-B/, ...
# remain committable.
docs/screenshots/uiux-pass/full-capture/
